values:
open your eyes a little wider.
can you see,
the pain,
the hurt,
every thing i hide secretly,
deep down inside of me,
can you?  can you see?
the crying every night,
just to avoid a simple fight,
can you see the injury,
that thing i hold,
deep down inside of me?
no? thats what i thought.
of course you wouldnt.

due to current events i have decided that it would best if i lock this journal. i am sick of people reading it and then harassing me the next day for being honest and simply documenting my life in the simplest of ways i can think of. that and because it has been brought to my attention that people who should not be sticking their nose in my business have been reading this. so i have decided that the only way to solve both problems is to lock this journal from all. i give my deepest apologies to those friends who did read my journal.

xoxo mandie xoxo
